Wealthy people in Singapore also use ValueMax branches, laying gold bars or Rolex watches that can yield up to 60 percent of their purchase value in cash.
We see clients from all walks of life.
"They include wealthy individuals who need to borrow short-term money for commercial projects or investments, or small businesses that need to overcome temporary monetary difficulties," says Ms. Yaah.
